# Test URLs for Svitlyna QOI image viewer
# Svitlyna is a QOI image viewer for UXN written in TAL
# These URLs test the viewer with various QOI showcase images using git URLs with query parameter arguments

#test_inject t^^10:emu^^buxn

## QOI showcase images with query parameter arguments
# Autumn image with original
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/autumn.qoi

# Cat image
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/cat.qoi

# Pixel mountain image
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/pixel-mountain.qoi

## Alternative format with explicit query parameter specification
# Testing different QOI images with the same viewer
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/autumn.qoi
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/cat.qoi
uxntal://git@https://github.com/gardenappl/svitlyna/blob/main/svitlyna.tal?!arg1=showcase/pixel-mountain.qoi

## Notes:
# - svitlyna.tal is the main QOI image viewer program
# - The ?!arg1=showcase/filename.qoi syntax passes the QOI file as an argument
# - This allows testing the viewer with different showcase images
# - QOI (Quite OK Image) format is a lossless image compression format
# - The showcase directory contains various test images in QOI format